 Proto made a smile. "I believe there is  a base down that way. I picked up 
its signal right before you crashed. Theres a large mass of maximals near it. 
Im guessing theres a battle going on. Im always in the mood for a fight." He 
liquidated and the transformed into Galvatron's silver Dragon mode. "You 
comin?" He spread his wings and flew towards the signal.
